The <a href="http://www.umass.edu/windenergy/" target="_blank">Wind Energy Center</a> (WEC) is part of the Mechanical 
Engineering department and has conducted industry-leading research in wind energy since the 1980's. Under the direction 
of Dr. James Manwell, students are exposed to a variety of research topics and engineering skills in preparation for a 
career in wind energy. RERL has graduated many leaders and engineers currently working in the wind energy industry.